  "detailed_description": "Ever wondered what life is like for a merchant in a role-playing game? Wonder no more! Experience life behind the counter in RPG Merchant, a VR game that lets you serve customers and face unexpected challenges with the help of a mysterious wizard. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/789290/extras/804df3d154747e62f8ef1c40e05c0cb4.poster.avif?t=1600289733\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/789290/extras/804df3d154747e62f8ef1c40e05c0cb4.webm?t=1600289733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/789290/extras/804df3d154747e62f8ef1c40e05c0cb4.mp4?t=1600289733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features: <br>- Run a store that sells weapons, potions, equipment and more! <br>- Defend against thieves and muggers <br>- Progress through increasingly difficult Story levels and Challenge Modes <br>- Take on Endless Mode to see how long you can last!<br><br><strong>NOTE: VR headset required!</strong>",
